import re

def extract_numeric_values(string):
    cleaned_string = re.sub('', '', string)
    numeric_values = re.findall('-?\\d+(?:\\.\\d+)?(?:[eE]-?\\d+)?', cleaned_string)
    return [float(value) for value in numeric_values]

import re

def extract_numeric_values(string):
    cleaned_string = re.sub('[^0-9.\\-e]', '', string)
    numeric_values = re.findall('', cleaned_string)
    return [float(value) for value in numeric_values]
